<hr />

<p>I have a position as Associate Professor (Distinguished Researcher Fellow) at the <a href="http://en.sjtu.edu.cn">Shanghai Jiao Tong University</a> in China.
My position is shared between the <a href="http://www.math.sjtu.edu.cn/">School of Mathematical Sciences</a> and the Shanghai Advanced Institute of Finance <a href="http://saif.sjtu.edu.cn">(SAIF)</a> within the China Academy of Finance and Research <a href="http://en.cafr.cn">(CAFR)</a>.</p>

<p>My research focus — even if not bounded to — are</p>

<ul>
  <li>Stochastic and Convex Analysis</li>
  <li>Decision Theory</li>
  <li>Risk and Uncertainty</li>
  <li>Data Analysis</li>
</ul>

